      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a complete service history. This is a rare opportunity to own an impeccably preserved example of this model that needs nothing but a new owner.",
