    {
      "id": "sybil_22_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_22",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, an exemplary specimen that balances sophisticated engineering with enduring value. Meticulously maintained and rigorously inspected, this automobile demonstrates remarkable mechanical integrity and a well-preserved aesthetic. It offers a refined driving experience, ensuring both reliability and prestige for the discerning owner. This selection represents a premier opportunity to acquire a high-caliber vehicle that has been curated to meet our exacting standards of quality and performance.",
      "price": 36850.0,
