      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my car, and it's honestly been such a reliable companion. It's in great shape and has been really well-cared for over the years\u2014perfect for someone who wants a smooth, worry-free ride without the brand-new price tag. It still looks sharp and drives beautifully! I'd love for you to come take it for a spin and see for yourself. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
