    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_21_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_21",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including high-pressure VANOS servicing and rear subframe reinforcement. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, paired with a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein dampers and polyurethane bushings for optimized kinematic response. The variable M differential lock ensures peak power delivery out of corners. A true driver-spec machine with a documented service history focusing on powertrain longevity and chassis rigidity.",
